      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;If we are talking about REALLY high end non-raiders doing VERY hard encounters for good loot, then I'd contend the ToB items ARE one groupable (and I bet you spend a lot less time getting ToB flagged and getting the kills down than the average raider took to get their first kill in demiplane).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Also groupable besides the ToB stuff (albeit difficult):&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=48758"&gt;http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=48758&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=48604"&gt;http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=48604&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=48744"&gt;http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=48744&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=47471"&gt;http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=47471&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=47472"&gt;http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=47472&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=47316"&gt;http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=47316&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=48746"&gt;http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=48746&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Almost all over 250 HP, almost all with decent focuses and effects, so that pretty much blows away the &amp;quot;75%&amp;quot; argument. Yeah I know, I know, &amp;quot;they are too hard, only raiders can do them, I only have 30 minutes a week to play, I only have a level 40 toon, I can't get a group, I want to solo them, it's not worth the time and effort because raiders get so much better&amp;quot; blah blah blah ad nauseum, but there ARE really great items out there to be had, and despite the difficulty, you'd STILL be putting in less time than the average raider to get your gear. Note that you can take yourself and five friends, go into a NON keyed, NON flagged, no prerequisite zone, and walk out 30 minutes to an hour later with BETTER loot than the average raider gets after months (to years) of flagging, backflagging, hoarding DKP, upgrading gear and guildies in order to survive, etc. I'd call that too easy, if anything.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
