&lt;P&gt;Another thing I think that the top tier raiders are forgetting is that it is in their own best interests to keep the gear gap between casual and raiders closer than it currently is. You should want guild applicants that are not totaly gimp unless you plan to only poach from other raiding guilds.&lt;BR&gt;&#xD;
