&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;The non-raiding applicants we have to our guild show up in nearly full GM armor, with DoD/PoR jewelry, the evolving cloak, etc. People who app with less are told to go gear up, then re-app. Its not like we don't get enough people apping, to be slightly selective.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;However, the thing to consider, is that anyone can gear up well enough in single group content, to be useful in a raid. Tanks have it hardest, but we've put a GM armored tank in the rotaton in tacvi/anguish/don and done just fine.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;And yes, we also get many apps from other guilds. We don't poach, as in actively recruiting from other guilds, but if they put in an app, and have dropped their old guild tag, then they are certainly considered.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
