hen again if such isn't available doesn't mean you wouldn't be happy with a skilled surgeon who happens to have never actually taken a bullet out if the alternative is just dying.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;But what is expressed in our app forum constantly is this. We can gear someone up. We can teach them what to do we can help them get keyed but we can not give them a good additude.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description>
